    <div>
      <p class="bigp rv">Most "AI" you've used is <span class="dim">a tool you pick up, ask a question, and put back down.</span> Osprey is the opposite. <span class="it">An operator that embeds inside the business permanently,</span> holds the whole portfolio in its head, and does the work. Not software you adopt. <span class="it">An operator you deploy.</span></p>
