    <div>
      <p class="bigp rv">A real Wednesday. <span class="it">Edited only for length.</span></p>
      <p class="tl-note rv d1">Every action is approvable, replayable, and tied to a policy you signed off on. Nothing happens without a paper trail.</p>
      <div class="tl">
